OL,3,CWoman with breast cancer waits more
OL,4,Cthan three months for vital treatment
OL,6,FA woman with stage three breast cancer
OL,7,Fhas told UTV she feels angry and let
OL,8,Fdown after waiting more than three
OL,9,Fmonths for chemotherapy treatment.
OL,11,FReferred urgently in November after
OL,12,Ffinding a lump, Claire Little's
OL,13,Ftreatment didn't start until mid-
OL,14,FFebruary, during which time the tumour
OL,15,Fhad grown.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
