CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1775678753
OL,3,CWoman with breast cancer waits more
OL,4,Cthan three months for vital treatment
OL,6,FClaire said: "When you see where some
OL,7,Fof the other money goes to in the NHS
OL,8,Fand you just think, as a female,
OL,9,Fyou're kind of pushed to the side.
OL,10,FIt's kind of like, 'oh, they'll just
OL,11,Fput up with it' and it becomes the
OL,12,Fnorm then."
OL,14,FClaire refuses to let her diagnosis
OL,15,Fdefine her joy, holding fast to the
OL,16,Fvibrant life she's always known.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1775678753
OL,3,CWoman with breast cancer waits more
OL,4,Cthan three months for vital treatment
OL,6,FShe said: "I dance every chemo session
OL,7,Fand I'll dance when I finish my chemo.
OL,8,FYou know what? Yeah, I've got cancer,
OL,9,Fbut life's still for living and I
OL,10,Fshould still live my life."
OL,12,FClaire also found vital support along
OL,13,Fthe way in a local community group,
OL,14,Fwhich brings together women navigating
OL,15,Fthe same uncertain journey.
OL,17,FAt Breast Mates in Newry, it's women
OL,18,Fsupporting women through diagnosis,
OL,19,Ftreatment, and beyond.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
