FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1775678753
OL,3,CWoman with breast cancer waits more
OL,4,Cthan three months for vital treatment
OL,6,FWomen in this support group have had
OL,7,Fsimilar experiences of waiting too
OL,8,Flong at every stage. So, when the
OL,9,Fsystem can't keep up, they do.
OL,11,FShazza Turley, Breast Mates Newry
OL,12,Fmember said: "Everything you could
OL,13,Fthink of that could happen to you,
OL,14,Fit's happened to somebody in the group.
OL,16,F"So there's always somebody to talk to
OL,17,Fand brings everybody together."
OL,19,FThis is where Claire found her support
OL,20,Fand it's within community groups like
OL,21,Fthis where strength is shared.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/5
